column2: Holder of the European Union Presidency (Chairmanship)
Since we are the chairman of the European Union, perhaps we should use that power to change the European Union focus to better suit our country's political & economic needs?

European Union Integration Focus to the EU members will not help their economy much.
European Union Research & Development Focus to the EU members will help their economy a little.
European Union Economic Focus to the EU members will help their economy a lot.
